Drawing app
Create a simple drawing app or coloring app.
Requirements
Touch controls for drawing and/or coloring
Could be a simple line drawing where the “pen” follows your finger trace OR pre-defined drawings that you can color / fill-in color the different sections
Ability to save drawing to an image on the device
Ability to share drawings as images from within the device
Must maintain a list of the drawings made and be able to re-access them when opening up the app to keep drawing
